column3: Eh yes this is old cruft, we certainly don't want to remove *label* commands from the help. \nYou've potentially saved me a hour of frustrating debugging for #7729.\nutACK https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/9894/commits/91321e63e0dbdabae682b7455329fded8aa576af.
